<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I loved Beautiful Ruins. It is not a book about travel. It is mostly a love story, beautifully written, with rich characters, humor and depth. I will <a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I loved Beautiful Ruins. It is not a book about travel. It is mostly a love story, beautifully written, with rich characters, humor and depth. I will remember it as one of my favorites, and will quickly find another book by Jess Walter. I am now a fan.<br /><a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
